                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              žRü* -3ü░M bg7550@gmail.comCMP-20260328-223609{"complaint_id": "CMP-20260328-223609", "subject": "a/c fixer", "complaint_raw": "Hi, I'm writing to file a complaint regarding the recent repair service performed by technician Mark Stevens on my A/C unit at 23 Joe Driove Cape Coral on March 31, 2026. Despite the service call costing $[Amount, e.g., 275] and being told the leak was fixed, the unit began leaking water again within 24 hours, causing water damage to my [affected area, e.g., hallway floor] and creating an inconvenience I shouldn't have to deal with after paying for a professional repair. I am requesting that a senior technician return to properly diagnose and fix the underlying issue at no additional cost, and that I receive a service voucher or partial refund to compensate for the inconvenience and property disruption. For immediate follow-up on this matter, I can be reached directly, and I have also noted the contact for supervision as bgalitsky@hotmail.com or 209-208-4065. I expect a response within 2 business days to schedule the corrective repair. Thank you.", "complaint_professional": "Hello,\n\nI am contacting you regarding the following unresolved customer issue:\n\nHi, I'm writing to file a complaint regarding the recent repair service performed by technician Mark Stevens on my A/C unit at 23 Joe Driove Cape Coral on March 31, 2026. Despite the service call costing $[Amount, e.g., 275] and being told 