tisfy demand"],    nment for Sofia. Thank you.", "complaint_professional": "Hello,\n\nI am contacting you regarding the following unresolved customer issue:\n\nHi, I'm writing to formally express my concern about the teaching approach of piano instructor David Chen, who has been giving weekly lessons to my child, Sofia, since January 2026. Over the past several sessions, Mr. Chen has repeatedly used dismissive and harsh languageŌĆösuch as telling Sofia she's \"not trying hard enough\" or sighing audibly when she makes simple mistakesŌĆöwhich has left her feeling anxious, discouraged, and reluctant to practice. We enrolled her in lessons to foster a love of music, but the current dynamic is having the opposite effect. I kindly request that [Music Academy Name] address this communication style and ensure instructors use patient, age-appropriate encouragement with young students. For follow-up, I understand the appropriate contact is the studio director at 209-270-9056. I hope we can work together to create a more positive and supportive learning environment for Sofia. Thank you.\n\nPlease review the issue, confirm the appropriate remedy, and provide a timeline for resolution.\n\nThank you.", "user_email": "bg7550@gmail.com", "user_name": "Boris Galitsky", "created_at": "2026-03-27T00:06:38", "docs": [], "evidence_pack_pdf": null, "strategy": {"primary_goal": "general resolution", "acceptable_fallbacks": ["refund/reimbursement", "credit/voucher"], "escalate_if": ["explicit denial", "no reply after follow-up", "ambiguous partial offer that does not satisfy demand"], "evidence_needed": []}, "current_status_summary": "Company agreed to satisfy the demand. Complaint resolved.", "final_conclusion": "The company is cooperating by assigning a new teacher as a remedy to the complaint, which is a concrete step towards resolution.", "auto_send_policy": "manual", "threads": {"19d2c9fee4d90595": {"thread_id": "19d2c9fee4d90595", "label": "company_support", "status": "resolved", "