 is needed\"\n  ]\n}"}}}, {"ts": "2026-03-28T22:38:11", "channel": "system", "kind": "decision", "title": "Drafted next step (draft_reply)", "detail": "Company appears to be offering a remedy; seek concrete confirmation and timeline.", "meta": {"thread_id": "19d369755c78f3ff", "stage": "resolution_check", "confidence": 0.76, "drafts": 1}}, {"ts": "2026-03-28T22:38:11", "channel": "email", "kind": "sent", "title": "Email sent", "detail": "Hello,\n\nThank you for your reply. Please confirm the exact remedy being provided, including amount/value and when it will be issued.\n\nRegards", "meta": {"thread_id": "19d369755c78f3ff", "gmail_msg_id": "19d369906c8b29f5", "gmail_thread_id": "19d369755c78f3ff", "subject": "[AGENT=company_support] Please confirm resolution details"}}, {"ts": "2026-03-28T22:40:39", "channel": "phone", "kind": "received", "title": "Phone call reply", "detail": "Yes, I understand and no additional repair needed at this time. It is not urgent, but uh, please consider the voucher value above 200. Thank you, bye.", "meta": {"thread_id": "19d369755c78f3ff"}}, {"ts": "2026-03-28T22:40:41", "channel": "system", "kind": "satisfaction", "title": "Satisfaction decision", "detail": "Company offers a voucher with a value above 200, which is an acceptable fallback outcome.", "meta": {"thread_id": "19d369755c78f3ff", "verdict": "resolved", "gpt_used": true, "signals": {"key_phrases": ["please consider the voucher value above 200"], "primary_goal": "refund/reimbursement", "acceptable_fallbacks": ["credit/voucher", "rebooking", "goodwill compensation"], "response_excerpt": "Yes, I understand and no additional repair needed at this time. It is not urgent, but uh, please consider the voucher value above 200. Thank you, bye.", "raw_model_output": "{\n  \"verdict\": \"resolved\",\n  \"reason\": \"Company offers a voucher with a value above 200, which is an acceptable fallback outcome.\",\n  \"key_phrases\": [\"please consider the voucher value above 200\"]\n}"}}}, {"ts